00:10:25.067 --> 00:10:26.359
Anda merusak kepercayaan saya.

00:10:26.734 --> 00:10:28.234
Aku sungguh minta maaf.

00:10:32.775 --> 00:10:35.484
Saya benar-benar tidak tahu.

00:10:35.610 --> 00:10:38.568
Mish membuat
kesalahan dan dia takut.

00:10:38.651 --> 00:10:40.318
